Subscription type: Customer (Number of users: <%= @trips.user_sub_type.find_by(subscription_type: "Customer").count %>, % of all users: <%= number_to_percentage((@trips.user_sub_type.find_by(subscription_type: "Customer").count / @trips.count.to_f) * 100) %>)</br>

